text: Lasiococca malaccensis is a species of plant in the family Euphorbiaceae. It is a tree endemic to Peninsular Malaysia. ==References== * Kochummen, K.M. 1998. Lasiococca malaccensis. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
